BETA-HAIRPIN -- GLOBAL CLUSTERING

Clustering parameters: fpoints=0.15 ; qs=1

Files needed: ../GLOBAL/colvar.wt.30cv.4 ref.idxs

Command to get the clusters and the PMIs: 

awk '{for(i=1;i<=14;i++)print $i,$(i+16)}' ../GLOBAL/colvar.wt.30cv.4 | ../../../bin/pamm -d 2 -p 6.28,6.28 -ngrid 5000 -readgrid ref.idxs -savevoronois -fpoints 0.15 -qs 1 -o fp0.15-qs1 -v

Build the adjacency: 

python2.7 ../../../tools/merge 2 fp0.15-qs1.grid fp0.15-qs1.bs
